sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI
    participant Config as RunnerConfig
    participant WB as WorkflowBuilder
    participant EB as EventBusBuilder
    participant RB as RunnerBuilder
    participant Runner
    participant Pipeline as WorkflowPipeline
    participant Discover as DiscoverStage
    participant Execute as ExecuteStage
    participant MW as MiddlewarePipeline
    participant Backend
    participant Bus as EventBus
    participant Store as Artifact/History Store
    participant Reporter

    User->>CLI: make test_all_local
    CLI->>Config: create config
    CLI->>RB: build backend + middleware
    RB-->>CLI: backend pipeline
    CLI->>EB: build event bus
    EB-->>CLI: event bus
    CLI->>WB: build workflow pipeline
    WB-->>CLI: workflow pipeline
    CLI->>Runner: Runner(pipeline)

    CLI->>Runner: run()
    Runner->>Pipeline: run(context)

    Pipeline->>Discover: execute(context)
    Discover-->>Pipeline: context.files

    Pipeline->>Execute: execute(context)

    loop each test file
        Execute->>Bus: publish test_started
        Execute->>MW: execute(request)
        MW->>Backend: execute(request)
        Backend-->>MW: TestResult
        MW-->>Execute: TestResult
        Execute->>Bus: publish test_finished
    end

    Execute-->>Pipeline: context.results

    Pipeline->>Store: save report / append history
    Pipeline->>Reporter: report(context.results)
    Pipeline-->>Runner: context
    Runner-->>CLI: context